author: Gina.T
title: Gina.T
text: I sold my Guns & Roses Ticket within 5 minutes of putting on Ticketmaster Resale! Wow! I was so impressed with the efficiency of their website, that I certainly wont hesitate to buy tickets from them in the future! What a brillant service they provide for consumers. Hey! If only all websites were like Ticketmasters Resale! We would all be Happy Chappys!
